column2: Does your employer provide mental health benefits as part of healthcare coverage?
column3: Do you know the options for mental health care available under your employer-provided coverage?
column4: Has your employer ever formally discussed mental health (for example, as part of a wellness campaign or other official communication)?
column5: Does your employer offer resources to learn more about mental health concerns and options for seeking help?
column6: Is your anonymity protected if you choose to take advantage of mental health or substance abuse treatment resources provided by your employer?
column7: If a mental health issue prompted you to request a medical leave from work, asking for that leave would be:
column8: Do you think that discussing a mental health disorder with your employer would have negative consequences?
column9: Do you think that discussing a physical health issue with your employer would have negative consequences?
column10: Would you feel comfortable discussing a mental health disorder with your coworkers?
column11: Would you feel comfortable discussing a mental health disorder with your direct supervisor(s)?
column12: Do you feel that your employer takes mental health as seriously as physical health?
column13: Have you heard of or observed negative consequences for co-workers who have been open about mental health issues in your workplace?
column14: Would you have been willing to discuss a mental health issue with your direct supervisor(s)?
column15: Do you feel that being identified as a person with a mental health issue would hurt your career?
column16: Do you think that team members/co-workers would view you more negatively if they knew you suffered from a mental health issue?
column17: How willing would you be to share with friends and family that you have a mental illness?
column18: Have you observed or experienced an unsupportive or badly handled response to a mental health issue in your current or previous workplace?
column19: Have your observations of how another individual who discussed a mental health disorder made you less likely to reveal a mental health issue yourself in your current workplace?
column20: Do you have a family history of mental illness?
column21: Have you had a mental health disorder in the past?
column22: Do you currently have a mental health disorder?
column23: Have you been diagnosed with a mental health condition by a medical professional?
column24: Have you ever sought treatment for a mental health issue from a mental health professional?
column25: If you have a mental health issue, do you feel that it interferes with your work when being treated effectively?
column26: If you have a mental health issue, do you feel that it interferes with your work when NOT being treated effectively?
column29: What country do you work in?
